ELB Engineering Services has been awarded the design and supply contract for the sugar supply system for Illovo Sugar Malawi’s Dwangwa packing facility, in Malawi. ELB will provide Illovo with a new sugar supply system that complies with the sugar producer’s hygiene requirements, while reducing dust and product losses. Illovo is Malawi’s largest sugar producer and also owns agricultural and milling assets at the Nchalo Sugar Estate.